DOC.brief_summary: A Placebo-controlled, Four Way Crossover Study to Investigate the Effect on QT/QTc Interval of a Single Dose of FYU-981, Compared with Placebo, Using Moxifloxacin as a Positive Control, in Healthy Male and Female Volunteers.
DOC.brief_title: Clinical Pharmacology of FYU-981 (Effect on QT/QTc Interval)
DOC.criteria: Japanese adult subjects Body mass index: >=18.5 and <27.5 Subjects with any disease or any history of diseases that might be unsuitable for participation in the clinical study
